<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="wake-v">wake <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /weɪk/    美 /weɪk/  </p>
<p>(woke /  woken)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>醒；醒来；醒着：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What time do you usually <strong>wake up</strong> in the morning?
你早晨通常几点醒？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>woke</strong> ( <strong>up</strong> ) to find himself alone in the house.
他醒来时，发现屋里只有自己一个人。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>唤醒；弄醒：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Very early in the morning, Uncle Paul woke us up to have breakfast.
一大清早，保罗叔叔把我们叫起来吃早饭。</p><footer>2018 浙江</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was woken by the sound of someone moving around.
有人来回走动，把我吵醒了。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="wake-up-to">wake up to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>意识到；认识到：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He hasn't yet woken up to the fact that the situation is serious.
他还没意识到形势严峻这个事实。</p></div></div>